# Apple-Grade UI Overhaul + Platform-Specific Music

## Goal
Transform NoProc into a world-class, Apple-grade productivity dashboard. Add platform-specific music controls, a settings panel with custom wallpaper/gradient support, and breathtaking aesthetics.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Platform-Specific Music**: Extension controls will only appear on desktop (>900px). Spotify miniplayer will only appear on mobile (<900px). Both will share the same metadata system.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Settings Panel**: A new full-screen overlay panel accessible from the sidebar gear icon. Users can pick live gradient presets or upload a custom wallpaper image (stored in localStorage as base64).

---

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Settings Panel (New Feature)

#### [NEW] [settings.js](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess!/NoProc/js/settings.js)
- `SettingsManager` class with [open()](file:///c:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess%21/NoProc/js/timer.js#104-115), `close()`, [save()](file:///C:/Users/admin/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/noproc/js/tasks.js#55-58), [load()](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess%21/NoProc/js/spotify.js#121-157)
- **Background Options**:
  - 6 curated live gradient presets (Aurora, Sunset, Ocean, Midnight, Nature, Custom)
  - Custom wallpaper upload via `<input type="file">` → base64 → localStorage
- **Platform detection**: `isMobile()` check using `window.innerWidth <= 900`
- Saves preferences to `localStorage`

#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess!/NoProc/index.html)
- Add Settings overlay `<div id="settings-overlay">` with gradient grid + wallpaper upload
- Add `data-platform="desktop"` / `data-platform="mobile"` attributes to music controls
- Enhance `<head>` with Apple-style meta tags

#### [NEW] [css/settings.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess!/NoProc/css/settings.css)
- Full-screen glass panel overlay styles
- Gradient preview cards, wallpaper upload area
- Smooth open/close animations

---

### 2. Platform-Specific Music Controls

#### [MODIFY] [app.js](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess!/NoProc/js/app.js)
- Add `detectPlatform()` method → shows/hides extension or Spotify controls
- Desktop: Show extension bridge control bar in sidebar footer
- Mobile: Show Spotify miniplayer at bottom
- Listen for `resize` events to re-evaluate

#### [MODIFY] [spotify.js](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess!/NoProc/js/spotify.js)
- Skip initialization if `window.innerWidth > 900` (desktop)
- Only load SDK and show login on mobile

---

### 3. Apple-Grade Aesthetic Overhaul

#### [MODIFY] [variables.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess!/NoProc/css/variables.css)
- Add SF Pro-inspired font stack fallback
- Refine color palette with Apple-style neutral grays + vivid accent
- Add gradient preset CSS custom properties

#### [MODIFY] [layout.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess!/NoProc/css/layout.css)
- Enhanced `bg-wrapper` to support both live gradients AND wallpaper images
- Wallpaper mode: `background-image` with cover + blur overlay
- Refined sidebar: Apple-style translucent pill navigation
- Clock: Apple Dynamic Island-inspired container

#### [MODIFY] [components.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess!/NoProc/css/components.css)
- Buttons: Gradient fills with hover bloom effects
- Cards: Frosted glass with inner light edges
- Timer: Apple Watch-style radial with glow stroke
- Miniplayer: Album-art-driven dynamic glow

#### [MODIFY] [animations.css](file:///C:/Users/admin/OneDrive/Documents/.Caesar%20Codess!/NoProc/css/animations.css)
- Spring physics curves for all transitions
- `@keyframes shimmer` for gradient cards
- Enhanced blob system with more organic movement
- Parallax-style scroll effects

