## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Resize browser to test platform detection (extension vs Spotify toggle)
- Open Settings → pick each gradient preset → verify live background change
- Upload a wallpaper image → verify it persists after refresh
- Test dark/light theme toggle with all gradient presets
- Mobile viewport: Confirm Spotify bar, no extension controls
- Desktop viewport: Confirm extension controls, no Spotify bar
